eplyTime":"2017-07-15T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"咁好機會都唔識把握。。。"},{"pid":"f4d1650616c14f543767fab21873dca25c71d8ff","tid":323211,"uid":28507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T22:52:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁好機會都唔識把握。。。</blockquote><br />\n冇機會 把乜握<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63739aeb69718dde57a1aa2d7c1247f47227819","tid":323211,"uid":28507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"每次唱K都好鍾意聽你唱<br />\n而今次同你唱個心就乸埋一舊咁(仲要有合唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n你係唱俾你鍾意嘅人聽 而我係唱俾你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我又要繼續一班人大癲大肺<br />\n上到車返屋企就自己心痛到世界末日<br />\n人地叫你名問你返到屋企未<br />\n我呢 我怯我驚我冇用 淨係識羨慕<br />\n每次對住感情都好懦弱唔識面對<br />\n點解你可以咁温柔咁好<br />\n點解半年前先第一次見面會可以咁沉迷<br />\n好想攬住你 好想每個時刻都有你<br />\n就算你唔鍾意我 我都係好鍾意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新髮色好啱你哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51df61ff2e6acbd619b016a81161d14a25ca431","tid":323211,"uid":13446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:22:43.000Z","msg":"鐘意人，點解唔試下會爭取？<br />\n無努力過唔好係到賴地硬，<br />\n了解下佢鐘意咩類型，<br />\n你自己係咪個一種類型？<br />\n係既，就去馬！"},{"pid":"466aaecfc96e1958e6b9da0c535ff41b4a799606","tid":323211,"uid":64756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:24:25.000Z","msg":"女人如衣服"},{"pid":"f08adef705a9f6a9c491c4ae8c030a3b1e083794","tid":323211,"uid":4852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:19:49.000Z","msg":"灑脫啲啦仆街<br />\n一係自爆一係放手喇好嘛?<br />\n你點叫春都好佢都唔會知﹐唔好懶係好委屈﹐咁落去辛苦嘅係自己<br />\n煩得感情事都係後生仔﹐仲有大把時間﹐今次就博一次啦"},{"pid":"de9063ac5ea60fa41a3eb73f90